                                <note>Top of page: Note in Swedish regarding the acquisition of the book, in black ink by a 19th-century hand: <quote xml:lang="sv">Skänkt till Kongl. Bibliotheket af Ryttmästaren P. von Möller. 20 Oct. 1871. Har tillhört Lüdekes boksamling. är skrifvet i Sverige 1450-1500.</quote> Lower left corner: National Library book label with the current signum in black ink.</note>
                            </p>
